  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Mentor the Vulnerable Girl Child to Impact 1000s</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Makomborero aims to see 1000s of girls stay in school through identifying vulnerable girls aged 13 - 14yrs and providing a Mentorship Programme that gives them hope and a vision for their futures beyond the social pressures they face.  We hope to address, the gender imbalance we experience with our scholarship programme and to see more girls making it through to Form 4 and not dropping out at Form 2. This project will be a project run by Makomborero past girl students.</narrative>
  </description>
